    "Then, the outputs of the program were processed into 18,533 grid boxes.",
    "A box containing the co-crystalized ligand in the original target structure is assigned a true label.",
    "The other boxes are labelled as negative.",
    "Finally, missing data was replaced with the average feature, also known as mean value imputation.Fig. 2 Representation of voxelisation processing for a protein (PDB ID: 1A3E) structure using PyMol.",
